[Student "S"]
{SOUTH thinks there might be slam if NORTH holds both minor Aces, so he tries Blackwood.

When NORTH shows just one Ace SOUTH is afraid he will have a trump loser as well, so 
he stops at 5\H.

It turns out that SOUTH might make twelve tricks, depending on the \HK situation.}

